	   <tr><td colspan=2>I got this earring about a year ago when I was playing a warrior, and it was for the event where we summoned Tunare in Lfay and Cazic Thule showed and cursed Equestrielle's horn. Firiona had to cut off the horn and now Eques is no longer a nice unicorn. I also got the name Matrumlus the Earth Keeper, which I should have said &quot;no&quot; to when asked if I wanted to keep it as I get tells constantly asking if I am a GM or how I got the name. Anyway, at the time this item was awesome and having had a cloak of flame as well I must say that the haste on this was substantially faster. Now they have added even more haste to this thing as of today's patch, and I don't even play this char anymore. Damn shame its no drop as I could prob sell for a TON. I play a bard now and while this would be nice for him I dont melee as much and would sell it if I had it. Oh well, maybe someday...<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Matumlus the Earth Keeper<br>aka <br>Kippen Valamor<br>Guardians of Valour<br>Thoulxe Paells</td></tr>
